{"tid":1563490,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"推介一部2004年既舊電影 《情獄》","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:49:42.000Z","uid":130303,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28770cddce6a82860cbb5d199cb31aa820954866","tid":1563490,"uid":130303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"故事講述男主角因為信用卡詐騙而入獄，係獄中俾一個囚犯裡面既大佬睇中，收男主角做佢條口靚 ，其實係想屌男主角屎忽。  囚犯大佬係獄中做賣毒品生意, 教男主角賣粉賺錢，但男主角鍾意另一個黑鬼囚犯, 成日偷偷地走去黑鬼監倉房同佢玩69, 最尾俾獄卒發現要接受懲罰。件事俾囚犯大佬知道咗就好嬲，同黑鬼係操場隻揪。係一個係監獄裡面既愛情故事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/12/dQKsgT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2FdQKsgT.jpg&h=d04119f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣點:<br />\n1.  全程打真軍演出，絕無借位造假<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.  男主角靚仔，神情帶點憂鬱，有梁朝偉feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.  實景拍攝，真實感充足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n缺點:<br />\n男主角鍾意既對象如果係靚仔鬼佬會更加好"},{"pid":"f078e654ccf8b188efdc3af4d94de9f602efdc9a","tid":1563490,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:04:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">對準政權 遍地開花</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2D3bRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2D3bRU.jpg&h=49b546b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXuufm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXuufm1.jpg&h=98681984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yM2WNBw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM2WNBw.jpg&h=9433ed2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zasf29R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzasf29R.jpg&h=aca10195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"